{"tid":1977021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[坡狗] 昨天新病例數字提前洩露 衛生部對此已報警處理","createTime":"2020-04-17T15:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T17:40:45.000Z","uid":95138,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"56da20a9fda1eee769a71cd5acbbdd6040e990eb","tid":1977021,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"昨天的冠病新病例數字提早約10小時走漏風聲，衛生部表示已針對此事報警，調查正在進行中。<br />\n<br />\n昨天（4月16日）出現的728起新病例是我國單日的最高紀錄，但衛生部晚上11時發文告公佈前，網上已流傳這個數字，一些社交媒體賬號甚至還報道了本地社區病例等細節。<br />\n<br />\n衛生部答復《聯合早報》詢問時指出，衛生部得知此事件，並已報警處理。警方正在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n根據官方機密法令，非法傳播官方資料的罪名一旦成立，肇事者將面對不超過2000元罰款和不超過兩年監禁。"},{"pid":"52a0ca1c5e975fcffd59800755b5fce45c9de3fc","tid":1977021,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⚠️<span style=\"color: red;\">請注意以下專搶新Po頭幾則留言，再屈樓主係五毛嘅新五毛會員</span>&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「好野可以出街lu」<br />\n</span><br />\n罪證<br />\n1. 胡亂屈樓主五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foJDuT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foJDuT</a><br />\n#2 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n2.胡亂屈樓主五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foyAsT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foyAsT</a><br />\n#4 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n3.明顯五毛言論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foJCJT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foJCJT</a><br />\n#4 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n4.明顯五毛言論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foJPdT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foJPdT</a><br />\n#8 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n5.承認自己係五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avuHgeV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avuHgeV</a><br />\n#19 回覆"},{"pid":"414dd079e596939c71ab7101cdd6cddf298a2d1a","tid":1977021,"uid":258578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:46:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4d958e2f0df0f808e3d37a49a133cde3cc0b973","tid":1977021,"uid":353228,"lik